<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.10.9">
<l>nampi yaitteṉ kuṟuṅkuṭi niṉṟavac</l>
<l>cempo ṉētika ḻuntiru mūrttiyai</l>
<l>yumpar vāṉava rātiyañ cōtiyai</l>
<l>yempi rāṉaiyeṉ colli maṟappaṉō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Nampi, the brilliant form that shines with that</l>
<l>red gold who stays in southern Kuṟuṅkuṭi,</l>
<l>the primordial effulgence of the celestials beyond,</l>
<l>our lord, saying what will I forget him?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
